{"tid":2319220,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[PC/PS/Xbox] Cyberpunk 2077 集中討論區(5) Welcome to Night City","createTime":"2020-12-10T02:43:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-10T09:09:54.000Z","uid":112814,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"429c57c9444494119be9e7e9f923ca7f4f2773e7","tid":2319220,"uid":112814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T02:43:40.000Z","msg":"<p class=\"center\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QGkqvGx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQGkqvGx.jpg&h=77395dc1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n動作冒險開放世界《電馭叛客 2077》將讓你深入沉溺於肉體改造、爭權奪利又紙醉金迷的巨型都市「夜城」。化身非法傭兵 V，尋找某種絕無僅有的植入物，掌握長生不死的關鍵。自由打造角色的生化改造裝置、技能及遊玩風格，並盡情探索一望無際的巨型城市，讓每一次抉擇逐步左右劇情與世界的走向。<br />\n<br />\nTrailer:<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ixl31324UxE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fixl31324UxE&d=DJHqE1tJ5F0S1%2BmpD1KYpkoInKkgZqzseva8eQDkMF8%3D&h=36fb3b3d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ixl31324UxE</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/BO8lX3hDU30\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FBO8lX3hDU30&d=DJHqE1tJ5F0S1%2BmpD1KYpkoInKkgZqzseva8eQDkMF8%3D&h=34b9c96b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/BO8lX3hDU30</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/UnA7tepsc7s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FUnA7tepsc7s&d=DJHqE1tJ5F0S1%2BmpD1KYpkoInKkgZqzseva8eQDkMF8%3D&h=0599fd91\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/UnA7tepsc7s</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n發售日: <br />\n<span class=\"medium\"><del>2020年4月16日<br />\n2020年9月17日<br />\n2020年11月19日</del></span><br />\n2020年12月10日<br />\n<br />\n夜城(Night City)網站<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.nightcity.love/zh-tw/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nightcity.love%2Fzh-tw%2F&d=DJHqE1tJ5F0S1%2BmpD1KYpkoInKkgZqzseva8eQDkMF8%3D&h=a2a835bb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.nightcity.love/zh-tw/</a><br />\n官方網站:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cyberpunk.net/hk/zh-tw/\" data-sr-u